props.align: Deprecated, use **align-\*** class. Available options are: **start**, **center**, **end**, **baseline** and **stretch**.
props.alignContent: Deprecated, use **align-content-\***. Available options are: **start**, **center**, **end**, **space-between**, **space-around** and **stretch**.
props.density: Adjusts the spacing between `v-col`s. Available options are: **default**, **comfortable**, **compact**.
props.justify: Deprecated, use **justify-\***. Available options are: **start**, **center**, **end**, **space-between** and **space-around**.
